{"tid":1307254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大醫學院研究：港人近月抑鬱比率達9.1%　梁卓偉：已屬「疫症」","createTime":"2019-07-11T13:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T13:05:12.000Z","uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bae1fb532271e891f8739110b0fba399c4d265ca","tid":1307254,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"港大醫學院研究：港人近月抑鬱比率達9.1%　梁卓偉：已屬「疫症」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港大學李嘉誠醫學院公共衞生學院今日（11日）公布一項精神健康調查，發現今年的6月至7月港人疑似抑鬱症的比率上升至9.1%，較2014年佔領中環運動期間的比率5.3%高，亦遠高於2011年至2014年間的1.3%；潛在自殺想法方面，亦由佔中時的3.6%上升至近日的4.6%。<br />\n<br />\n港大醫學院院長梁卓偉形容在流行病學而言，是「精神健康因嚴重社會事故的疫症」，但未必有有效疫苗，社會應要聆聽及理解年輕人的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/350676/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8%E9%99%A2%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%88%E6%8A%91%E9%AC%B1%E6%AF%94%E7%8E%87%E9%81%949-1-%E6%A2%81%E5%8D%93%E5%81%89-%E5%B7%B2%E5%B1%AC-%E7%96%AB%E7%97%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F350676%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E9%2599%25A2%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25BF%2591%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%258A%2591%25E9%25AC%25B1%25E6%25AF%2594%25E7%258E%2587%25E9%2581%25949-1-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%258D%2593%25E5%2581%2589-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%25B1%25AC-%25E7%2596%25AB%25E7%2597%2587&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjibpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=d3cace71\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/350676/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8%E9%99%A2%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%88%E6%8A%91%E9%AC%B1%E6%AF%94%E7%8E%87%E9%81%949-1-%E6%A2%81%E5%8D%93%E5%81%89-%E5%B7%B2%E5%B1%AC-%E7%96%AB%E7%97%87</a>"}]}